---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Cat Gear Tools" description="Use practical calculators for cat litter cost, litter box sizing, and recurring maintenance planning.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Tools</span>
    <h1>Calculators that make product comparisons concrete.</h1>
    <p>Tools create a reason to return, share, and bookmark the site. The first tool models recurring litter cost.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section tool-grid">
    <a class="tool-card" href="/tools/litter-cost-calculator/">
      <span>01</span>
      <h2>Litter Cost Calculator</h2>
      <p>Estimate monthly and yearly litter cost by cat count, bag price, bag weight, and usage rate.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="tool-card disabled" href="/tools/">
      <span>02</span>
      <h2>Litter Box Size Selector</h2>
      <p>Planned: recommend minimum inner dimensions from cat length, weight, and mobility needs.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="tool-card disabled" href="/tools/">
      <span>03</span>
      <h2>Fountain Filter Cost</h2>
      <p>Planned: compare replacement filter cycles and yearly maintenance cost.</p>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
